00:03:02,723 --> 00:03:04,923
Aku agen khusus Lydia Clarkson.

17
00:03:05,166 --> 00:03:07,526
Aku akan menangani kasusmu.

18
00:03:07,650 --> 00:03:09,530
Mereka butuh bantuan.

19
00:03:14,019 --> 00:03:16,299
<i>Kau telah menjalani pemeriksaan kesehatan.</i>

20
00:03:16,463 --> 00:03:19,223
<i>Selain beberapa memar dan dehidrasi,</i>

21
00:03:19,467 --> 00:03:21,707
- kondisimu sangat baik.
